<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.10.2">
<l>kuṇṭalam tāḻak kuḻaltāḻa nāṇtāḻa</l>
<l>eṇticai yōrumi ṟaiñcit toḻutētta</l>
<l>vaṇṭamar pūṅkuḻa lārtukil kaikkoṇṭu</l>
<l>viṇtōy marattāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭavum tārāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While those of the eight directions</l>
<l rend="indent">bow and worship and priase [him]</l>
<l rend="indent"> as [his] earrings and curls and necklace [all] hang low,</l>
<l>He steals the fine clothes of those with flowered curls laden with bees.</l>
<l>Because of him in the tree that touches the sky</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end.</l>
<l>Because of him who won’t give us what we want,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
